5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:343:\"Today we are happy to announce that we have another 8 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are &#8211; Lotus flower, Soho Hotel, Samba, Haxon, Profession, Parlament, Cleanspace, Phomedia. If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Dominykas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9546:\"<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have another 8 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are &#8211; <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lotus-flower-flexible-multipurpose-shop-theme/5960164\" target=\"_blank\">Lotus flower</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/soho-hotel-responsive-hotel-booking-wp-theme/5576098\" target=\"_blank\">Soho Hotel</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/samba-colored-wordpress-theme/5691055\" target=\"_blank\">Samba</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/haxon-responsive-business-theme/5604180?WT.ac=search_item&amp;WT.seg_1=search_item&amp;WT.z_author=PixFlow\" target=\"_blank\">Haxon</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/profession-one-page-cv-responsive-theme/5773519?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=PixFlow\" target=\"_blank\">Profession</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/parlament-political-wordpress-theme/6056707\" target=\"_blank\">Parlament</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cleanspace-retina-ready-business-wp-theme/3776000\" target=\"_blank\">Cleanspace</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/phomedia-wordpress-theme-a-wp-ecommerce-theme/671247\" target=\"_blank\">Phomedia</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lotus flower theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lotus-flower-flexible-multipurpose-shop-theme/5960164\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/lotus_flower.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Lotus Flower is a flexible multi-purpose shop template suitable for any business (ecommerce, corporate, agency, portfolio and blog websites). Integrated with WooCommerce allows you to easily start your online store right away. Lotus Flower is easy to customize through its page builder included in the lollum framework.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lotus-flower-flexible-multipurpose-shop-theme/5960164\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Lotus flower</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Soho Hotel theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/soho-hotel-responsive-hotel-booking-wp-theme/5576098\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/soho_hotel.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Soho Hotel theme designed for hotels, hostels, service apartments and any other kind of accommodation which requires a booking system. Some features of Soho Hotel are: room availability checker, testimonials and PayPal payments.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/soho-hotel-responsive-hotel-booking-wp-theme/5576098\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Soho Hotel</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Samba theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/samba-colored-wordpress-theme/5691055\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/samba.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Samba is a responsive multi-purpose theme suitable for any business (corporate, agency, portfolio and blog websites). It features portfolio, 60+ background patterns, 4 sidebars and demo content.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/samba-colored-wordpress-theme/5691055\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Samba</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Haxon theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/haxon-responsive-business-theme/5604180?WT.ac=search_item&amp;WT.seg_1=search_item&amp;WT.z_author=PixFlow\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/haxon.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Haxon is a clean business theme which comes with several default page templates like home, portfolio, contact and etc. You can change Haxon’s theme general color using it’s control panel to any color you like. You can introduce your business or team in a beautiful home navigation area with great functionality.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/haxon-responsive-business-theme/5604180?WT.ac=search_item&amp;WT.seg_1=search_item&amp;WT.z_author=PixFlow\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Haxon</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Profession theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/profession-one-page-cv-responsive-theme/5773519?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=PixFlow\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/profession.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Profession is a one page CV WordPress theme with unlimited colors and 8 preset colors. You can have online resume with home, portfolio, resume and contact section. This theme also comes with a clean blog. Profession’s default layout is horizontal on desktop screens and changes to vertical layout in tablets and smart phones.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/profession-one-page-cv-responsive-theme/5773519?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=PixFlow\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Profession</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Parlament theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/parlament-political-wordpress-theme/6056707\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/parlament.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Parlament is a political WordPress theme which features interactive design, responsive implementation and a focus on user experience, usability and performance. The theme also features theme customizer, color options and smooth scrolling.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/parlament-political-wordpress-theme/6056707\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Parlament</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Cleanspace theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cleanspace-retina-ready-business-wp-theme/3776000\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/cleanspace.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>CleanSpace is a clean style and multi-purpose wordpress theme powered by pagebuilder. It is suitable for any kind of web sites, either it is a corporate/business site or it is a hair salon or portfolio site. The theme has variety of pages, starting from 4 home page layouts and ending with different portfolio and blog layouts.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/cleanspace-retina-ready-business-wp-theme/3776000\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Cleanspace</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"te