;a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Dominykas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6671:\"<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have another 5 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are &#8211; <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/emode-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/4355567?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Emode</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/ultra-web-studio-blog-portfolio-wordpress-theme/121611?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Ultra Web Studio</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/evolve-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/3813176?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Evolve</a>, <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lens-an-enjoyable-photography-wordpress-theme/5713452?WT.ac=search_item&amp;WT.seg_1=search_item&amp;WT.z_author=pixelgrade\" target=\"_blank\">Lens</a>, <a href=\"http://www.serverwp.com\" target=\"_blank\">ServerWP</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Themes \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Emode theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/emode-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/4355567?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278692\" alt=\"emode\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/emode.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Emode is a responsive WordPress theme with a few different skins. This theme is suitable for all businesses, corporations and creative portfolio sites. Some features of Emode are: portfolio and galleries, 7 custom widgets, drag and drop manager.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/emode-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/4355567?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Emode</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ultra Web Studio theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/ultra-web-studio-blog-portfolio-wordpress-theme/121611?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278693\" alt=\"ultrawebstudio\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ultrawebstudio.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Ultra Web Studio is suitable for a corporate/brandable site and also for personal portfolio and blog. It contains 14 different skins, revolution slider, custom widgets and a sleek nice design.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/ultra-web-studio-blog-portfolio-wordpress-theme/121611?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Ultra Web Studio</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Evolve theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/evolve-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/3813176?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278694\" alt=\"evolve\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/evolve.jpg\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Evolve is a simple theme with a clean layout. This theme is suitable for a brandable site and also for personal blog. It comes with the theme options panel, so it’s easy to customize.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/evolve-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/3813176?WT.ac=portfolio_item&amp;WT.seg_1=portfolio_item&amp;WT.z_author=Softwebmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Evolve</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lens theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lens-an-enjoyable-photography-wordpress-theme/5713452?WT.ac=search_item&amp;WT.seg_1=search_item&amp;WT.z_author=pixelgrade\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278695\" alt=\"lens\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lens.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>LENS theme is aimed at photographers in need for a solution that focuses on what matters most to them: their work. LENS delivers nice animated page transitions, fast but at the same time super smooth.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lens-an-enjoyable-photography-wordpress-theme/5713452?WT.ac=search_item&amp;WT.seg_1=search_item&amp;WT.z_author=pixelgrade\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Lens</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">ServerWP theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.serverwp.com\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-80782\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278696\" alt=\"serverwp\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/serverwp.png\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>ServerWP is designed with web hosts and businesses in mind. It features a huge array of color, font, and layout options which let you change the site.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.serverwp.com\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase ServerWP</a></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"http://wpml.org/2013/10/week-compatible-emode-ultra-web-studio-evolve-lens-serverwp/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data